nk" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text=
-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color=
: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Regions Fin=
ancial Corp.</a>=C2=A0But here is a more complicated <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32671930.258424/aHR0cHM6Ly9pbnZlc3RvcnMu=
c3RhdGVzdHJlZXQuY29tL2ludmVzdG9yLW5ld3MtZXZlbnRzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2VzL25ld3M=
