bably the SEC worries a little about Bitcoin custody =E2=80=94=C2=A0but it =
seems like a solvable problem for Bitcoins in a way that it isn=E2=80=99t f=
or wheat.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If you want to do a=C2=
