very $1 the underlying asset goes up =E2=80=94=C2=A0you probably have to do=
 that with derivatives too.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you run a Bitcoin futures ETF, and you see =
the spot Bitcoin ETFs coming for you, are you at least considering opening =
a 2x levered Bitcoin ETF? I=E2=80=99m sure the SEC would love that.</p>
