<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">There were a lot of investors with a =
lot of money looking for yield, and not that much yield available.</li>=09<=
li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Therefore, when companies wanted to borrow=
