indentures) that were favorable to them. Loans were often =E2=80=9Ccovenant=
-lite,=E2=80=9D and the documents often allowed companies to do various tri=
cky maneuvers that would <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/32671930.258424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGlj=
bGVzLzIwMjItMDQtMDcvZGlzdHJlc3NlZC1kZWJ0LWRlYWwtbWFrZXMtcGVvcGxlLW1hZD9jbXB=
