 style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Every so often lenders would notice, and com=
plain, and push back, and sometimes even win =E2=80=94=C2=A0some of the mos=
t egregious terms proposed by borrowers were <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/32671930.258424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNv=
bS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTctMDEtMTIvYm9uZC1jb3ZlbmFudHMtYW5kLXNrZXB0aWM=
