<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a private banker whose job is lendi=
ng money to wealthy people, one part of the job is being ingratiating and c=
harming and polite to the wealthy people so they will want to borrow money =
from you, and another part of the job is, when they ask to borrow money, ac=
tually getting them the money quickly and with a minimum of inconvenience. =
The first part of the job is probably easier to select and train for, but t=
he second part is probably more useful for the clients.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is a fun <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/32671930.258424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbm=
